doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    meta(name='description', content='How Purple Vector Operations works with clinics across Tasmania, from initial review and scoping through implementation, delivery, support, and secure handling.')
    meta(name='author', content='Purple Vector Operations')
    title Process | Purple Vector Operations
    link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
    script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

  body#page-top
    nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
      .container
        a.navbar-brand(href='index.html')
          img(src='assets/img/navbar-logo.svg', alt='Purple Vector Operations')
        button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          | Menu
          i.fas.fa-bars.ms-1
        #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.ms-auto.py-4.py-lg-0
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='index.html') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='about.html') About
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='services.html') Services
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.active(href='process.html') Process
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='faq.html') FAQ
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='index.html#contact') Contact

    header.masthead(style='padding-top: 12rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;')
      .container
        .masthead-subheading How PVO works
        .masthead-heading.text-uppercase A practical process for real clinics
        p.text-white-50.mx-auto(style='max-width: 760px;')
          | The goal is not to drown a clinic in jargon and workshops. The goal is to figure out what is slowing things down, fix it sensibly, and leave the place more usable than it was before.

    section.page-section
      .container
        .text-center
          h2.section-heading.text-uppercase The process
          h3.section-subheading.text-muted Clear enough to be reassuring. Flexible enough to survive reality.
        ul.timeline
          li
            .timeline-image
              h4 Step 1
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Initial review
                h4.subheading Understand the current setup
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted Review the practice's software, workflows, pain points, admin load, record handling, access issues, and operational priorities before recommending any work.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4 Step 2
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Scope and structure
                h4.subheading Choose the right engagement model
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted Work may be structured as an ongoing retainer, a one-off project, a digitisation program, or targeted support depending on what the clinic actually needs.
          li
            .timeline-image
              h4 Step 3
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Implement and tidy
                h4.subheading Fix the operational mess
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted This can include workflow cleanup, Xestro support, template preparation, document organisation, scanning, automation, and practical support that staff can realistically maintain.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4 Step 4
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Deliver and document
                h4.subheading Leave things usable
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted Changes, files, and processes are documented clearly so the clinic is not left relying on mystery knowledge or improvised fixes.
          li
            .timeline-image
              h4 Step 5
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Ongoing support
                h4.subheading Keep improving what matters
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted For retained clients, support continues through routine checks, problem-solving, incremental improvements, and practical help as the clinic changes.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Built
                br
                | For
                br
                | Clinics

    section.page-section.bg-light
      .container
        .row.g-4
          .col-lg-6
            .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
              .card-body.p-4
                h3.card-title.text-uppercase.mb-3 What this can include
                ul.text-muted.mb-0
                  li Practice workflow review
                  li Xestro configuration and support
                  li Paper-to-digital batch planning
                  li Secure document handling and naming rules
                  li Template cleanup and process documentation
                  li Coordination with existing clinic IT providers
          .col-lg-6
            .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
              .card-body.p-4
                h3.card-title.text-uppercase.mb-3 What this does not include
                ul.text-muted.mb-0
                  li Clinical advice or medical decision-making
                  li Medico-legal judgment
                  li Replacing the clinic's staff with weird automation fantasies
                  li Taking over infrastructure outside the agreed scope

    section.page-section
      .container
        .row.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-10
            .text-center.mb-4
              h2.section-heading.text-uppercase For records digitisation projects
              h3.section-subheading.text-muted The chain-of-custody stuff people should care about.
            .row.g-4
              .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
                  .card-body.p-4
                    h4.text-uppercase Collection
                    p.text-muted Files can be collected in sealed, labelled containers with optional chain-of-custody logging for batches where requested.
              .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
                  .card-body.p-4
                    h4.text-uppercase Conversion
                    p.text-muted Records are scanned, OCR processed, named, checked, and organised into usable digital structures with human review.
              .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
                  .card-body.p-4
                    h4.text-uppercase Return and delivery
                    p.text-muted Completed files are returned through agreed secure methods, and original paper records are returned to the clinic.

    section.page-section.bg-light
      .container
        .row.justify-content-center.text-center
          .col-lg-8
            h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Want to start with a small piece?
            p.text-muted.mb-4 Many clinics start with one backlog, one workflow problem, or one messy software issue and expand from there.
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase.me-3(href='services.html') View Services
            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='index.html#contact') Contact PVO

    footer.footer.py-4
      .container
        .row.align-items-center
          .col-lg-4.text-lg-start Copyright © Purple Vector Operations 2026
          .col-lg-4.my-3.my-lg-0
            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='mailto:admin@purplevectoroperations.com', aria-label='Email Purple Vector Operations')
              i.fas.fa-envelope
          .col-lg-4.text-lg-end
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none.me-3(href='about.html') About
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none.me-3(href='services.html') Services
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none.me-3(href='process.html') Process
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none(href='faq.html') FAQ

    script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
    script(src='js/scripts.js')
